    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Ready to hit the road with confidence? This car is in good condition \u2014 it runs smoothly, handles daily driving with ease, and has clearly been well cared for over the years. You'll find it starts reliably, drives comfortably, and is ready for your everyday adventures without any major concerns. There's normal wear consistent with its age, but nothing that takes away from its solid, dependable performance. A great opportunity to get a quality vehicle at a fair price!",
