    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "2021 Honda Accord in poor condition. The interior has significant wear including torn or heavily damaged upholstery, staining, and damaged trim. Controls and displays may have functional issues. The exterior shows noticeable damage including dents, scratches, or rust. Mechanical issues are present and the car will likely require repairs before reliable daily use. Sold as-is.",
